  "text": "In studies that did consider more than one process, the picture was more complex and also showed, in addition to environmental filtering, the influence of dispersal limitation and/or species interaction. This concerns not only gastropod communities in Lake Ohrid and in other ancient lakes such as Lake Tanganyika [CITATION_1] , but also communities in freshwater systems in general [CITATION_2] .",
